    "course_title": "INTRODUCTION TO BIG DATA SYSTEMS",
    "description": "Deploy and use distributed systems to store and analyze large datasets.  Unstructured and structured approaches to storage will be covered.  Analysis will involve learning new query languages, processing streaming data, and training machine learning models.  Most programming will be done in Python.",
